Today, Mojang - the company responsible for the indie smash-hit Minecraft - is one year old! They have come a long way from humble beginnings; starting with only one man, and rapidly growing into a team of 11, Mojang has worked hard over the last year to raise their fledgling sandbox building game into something much greater - and they aren't showing any signs of slowing down. Great job guys, and happy birthday!

Today isn't just Mojang's birthday - we are also celebrating the birthday of our own WedTM! One of the co-founders of the Minecraft Forums, he has worked tirelessly alongside Citricsquid to make these forums the best they can be. Happy birthday, WedTM!














